Interface PsiReferenceList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iconable, PsiElement, UserDataHolder
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GrExtendsClause, GrImplementsClause, GrReferenceList, GrThrowsClause
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClsReferenceListImpl, GrExtendsClauseImpl, GrImplementsClauseImpl, GrReferenceListImpl, GrSyntheticReferenceList, GrThrowsClauseImpl, GrTypeParameterParameterExtendsListImpl, LightEmptyImplementsList, LightReferenceList, LightReferenceListBuilder, PsiReferenceListImpl

    public interface PsiReferenceList
extends PsiElement
    Represents a list of Java classes referenced by the implements, extends, throws, or with clause.
    See Also:
    PsiClass.getExtendsList(), PsiClass.getImplementsList(), PsiMethod.getThrowsList(), PsiProvidesStatement.getImplementationList()
